"          <div id=\"repoResult\" style=\"margin-top:10px;font-size:13px;\"></div>\n"
"          <div class=\"cr-panel-note\">Downloads happen in the background. Files are saved per-format to cheats/json, cheats/shn, cheats/mc4. The page remains responsive during download.</div>\n"
